result.name: Fishing Heya Japanese Restaurant

reviews.text: We ordered from the la carte menu and it was still at bargain price.  However,  the quality of fish and Japanese rice were really average....   The young waiters were helpful and efficiency but the owner (the guy with glasses and the lady)  weren't as good as the staff.
Fresh sashimi, tasty crab porridge. Sweet cocktails. Great variety of food items to choose from. Lamb is very delicious and must try! Definitely value for money. Will come again one day :)

This is one of the rare gems in TKO. Food is ok given it’s price and if you don’t wanna go out of the neighborhood this is the place to go. You got a great variety and drinks are good too. Can be crowded during weekends though, booking is recommended.
The CP value of this restaurant is quite high, nice and delicious dish. Give it a try if you like to eat Japanese food. Check out my photos for the food!
Nice food and very good servive

result.name: 漁之部屋日本料理

reviews.text: We ordered from the la carte menu and it was still at bargain price.  However,  the quality of fish and Japanese rice were really average....   The young waiters were helpful and efficiency but the owner (the guy with glasses and the lady)  weren't as good as the staff.
有時會漏單 上菜速度一般
經常漏單，點了又不來，不知是有心定無意！
雖然食物質素幾好，但樓面職員很唔掂，成日弄錯枱號，把我們叫的食物送錯隔離枱，害我們白等，弄得溜單情況很嚴重。。很多明明點了的食物都無來到無食到。
好，抵食。禮貌唔錯
